column5: Hit the Mad this morning, saw 5 fish but no hook-ups until we got this one to stick on a cowgirl over a flat that was about 5 feet deep.
Nice way to start the year congrats Tight Lines SBK
Nice going MW it's nice to see some slime.
Sweet.   What a great way to start the season.   Congrats
Nice musky. It's a great waterway top to bottom !
Nice fish Bud !!!!  Great way to open the season
Nice to get the first one of the season in the boat.
Nice.  Choosing to fish a river was a smart idea today, but man the fish were active.
Congrats on the 1st musky of the season and I spose also the 1st one posted on OFC  this year too.  Good luck for the rest of the season.
Nice catch...  The only one we hooked up on buried in the weeds and got off...
Nice musky! Didn't get one this weekend but I did end up catching a new personal best pike.
